Summary
  Specifies how the background of a list box is filled.
Description
  Use the TJvListboxFillMode type to specify how the background of a list box is filled.
@@TJvListboxFillMode.bfmTile
  The bitmap is drawn without changing its size, but the whole canvas will
  be filled with it. So it may be drawn several times next to each other.
  Use this setting if you use a texture bitmap, for example.
@@TJvListboxFillMode.bfmStretch
  This mode stretches the bitmap to the size of the canvas, which means that
  the bitmap will only be drawn once on the background.
See Also
  TJvCustomListBox.Background, TJvListBoxBackground.FillMode
